						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and built in at the right end. It seems to record a gift of gold by one Sōmāsi Sāmi for burning a perpetual lamp in the temple of Śrīpondai-[Perumānaḍigāḷ ?] at <hi rend="bold">Rājamalla-chaturvēdimaṅgalam</hi> besides a land gift made for another lamp evidently by a different person.</p>						

